quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  83,7,sun rakho ke badkaron ke aamaal sajeen mein hain
  83,8,aur tumkiya jantay hon ke sajeenkiya cheez hai ?
  83,9,aik daftar hai likha howa
  83,10,is din jhutlanay walon ki kharabi hai
  83,11,( yani ) jo insaaf ke din ko jutlatay hain
  83,12,aur is ko jhutlata wohi hai jo hadd se nikal jaane wala gunehgaar hai
  83,13,jab is ko hamari ayatain sunai jati hain to kehta hai ke yeh to aglay logon ke afsaanay hain
  83,14,dekho yeh jo ( aamaal bad ) karte hain un ka un ke dilon par zang baith gaya hai
  83,15,be shak yeh log is roz apne perwar-digaar ( ke deedar ) se oot mein hon ge
  83,16,phir dozakh mein ja daakhil hon ge
  83,17,phir un se kaha jaye ga ke yeh wohi cheez hai jis ko tum jutlatay they
  83,18,( yeh bhi ) sun rakho ke naiko karon ke aamaal aleen mein hain
  83,19,aur tum kokiya maloom ke aleenkiya cheez hai ?
  83,20,aik daftar hai likha howa
  83,21,jis ke paas Maqarrab ( farishtay ) haazir rehtay hain
  83,22,be shak naik log chain mein hon ge
  83,23,takhton par baithy hue nazare karen ge
  83,24,tum un ke cheharon hi se raahat ki taazgee maloom kar lau ge
  83,25,un ko khalis sharaab srbmhr pilayi jaye gi
  83,26,jis ki mohar mushk ki ho gi to ( nematon ke ) shaiqeen ko chahiye ke isi se raghbat karen
  83,27,aur is mein Tasneem ( ke pani ) ki ameezash ho gi
  83,28,woh aik chashma hai jis mein se ( khuda ke ) Maqarrab piyeen ge
  83,29,jo gunehgaar ( yani kufar ) hain woh ( duniya mein ) mominon se hansikiya karte they
  83,30,aur jab un ke paas se guzarte to hiqarat se isharay karte
  83,31,aur jab apne ghar ko lottay to itratay hue lottay
  83,32,aur jab un ( mominon ) ko dekhte to kehte ke yeh to gumraah hain
  83,33,halaank woh un par nigaran bana kar nahi beje gay they
  83,34,to aaj momin kafiroon se hansi karen ge
